Information received on [and dated] 6 Mar 2015 from Dr Bolortuya Purevsuren, OIE delegate, Veterinary and Animal Breeding Agency, Ministry for Industry and Agriculture, Ulaanbaatar, Mongolia

Summary
Report type: immediate notification
Date of start of the event: 25 Feb 2015
Date of pre-confirmation of the event: 4 Mar 2015
Reason for notification: reoccurrence of a listed disease
Date of previous occurrence: 4 Apr 2014
Manifestation of disease: clinical disease
Causal agent: food and mouth disease virus
Serotype: Pending
Nature of diagnosis: clinical, laboratory (advanced)
This event pertains a defined zone within the country.

New outbreaks (4)
Outbreak 1: Dood nariin, Bayansudal, Bulgan soum, Khovd
Date of start of the outbreak: 25 Feb 2015
Outbreak status: continuing (or date resolved not provided)
